---
title: Seared Salmon & Chive Butter Sauce with Steamed Veggies & Potato Mash
description: Sometimes, great cooking is a flurry of clever techniques and a dizzying array of ingredients. Other times, it’s the simplicity of
just a few things; chives, butter, lemon, potatoes and a beautifully cooked salmon.
